post slug meta box "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
==================================================================

NAME
----

post slug meta box - Display slug form fields.

SYNOPSIS
--------

Display slug form fields.

PARAMETERS
----------

 `$post` 
:   ([*object*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Object "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*)
    Default: *None*

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [2.6](/Version_2.6 "Version 2.6")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

post\_slug\_meta\_box() is located in `wp-admin/includes/meta-boxes.php`

